          style="--delay: 0.4s"
        >
          Marko Stankovic
        </h1>

        <p
          class="hero-enter text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-[#888888] font-light mb-8 cursor-blink"
          style="--delay: 0.7s"
        >
          Game Developer
        </p>

        <p
          class="hero-enter text-[#888888] text-lg max-w-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed"
          style="--delay: 0.85s"
        >
          I love writing the systems that make games feel alive — AI state
          machines that think, procedural worlds that surprise, editor tools
          that get out of the way. Three years of that in Unity&nbsp;3D, Unreal
          Engine, and Godot. Based in Serbia, open to remote.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-enter flex flex-wrap gap-4" style="--delay: 1s">
          <a
            href="#contact"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-[#00FFC8] hover:bg-[#00FFD0] text-[#0D0D0D] rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-150"
          >
            Let's Talk
          </a>
          <a
            href="#projects"
            class="px-6 py-3 border border-[#1F1F1F] hover:border-[#888888] text-[#888888] hover:text-[#F0F0F0] rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-150"
