          for and stayed with.
        </p>

        <!-- Primary engine cards -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
          <!-- Unity 3D -->
          <div
            class="skill-card reveal bg-[#141414] border border-[#1F1F1F] rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-violet-800/60 transition-colors duration-150"
